trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse"></xref> class is sent by the server as a response to a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest"></xref> object.

This response contains zero or more <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultEntry"></xref> objects, and zero or more <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference"></xref> objects.

The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse.Controls"></xref> property contains the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl"></xref> object returned by the server.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl"></xref> object returned by the server.

The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse.Entries"></xref> property contains a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultEntryCollection"></xref> object that contains the entries returned by the search.
A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultEntryCollection"></xref> object that contains the entries returned by the search.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse.ErrorMessage"></xref> property contains the error message, if any, for this operation.
The error message, if any, for this operation.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse.MatchedDN"></xref> property contains the matched distinguished name returned by the server.
The matched distinguished name returned by the server.

The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse.References"></xref> property contains a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection"></xref> object that contains search references returned by the server.
A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection"></xref> object that contains search references returned by the server.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse.Referral"></xref> property contains the server referrals.

The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse.ResultCode"></xref> property contains a value of <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ResultCode"></xref> that specifies the result code for the operation.
The result code for the operation.
